        "timestamp": "2018-04-01 09:57:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8: Code-Review-1\n\nI'm failing to understand the fix. Asking others to review. Trying to understand the root cause in the meantime.",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "7f933e571dafc2ead4f304cd63a4e294b718b698",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2119,
          "name": "Oren Haim Zvi Kleks",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "orenkleks@hotmail.com",
          "username": "shrek2000"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-04-08 05:17:56.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8: Code-Review-1\n\nI think that the root cause is that validationVsp is static. This forces this value to be shared between different sessions. Why is it static?",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "27fcc05e0f69f41acd1b7b0c52b17e545c63e450",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 1741,
          "name": "Avi Gaffa",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "avi.gaffa@amdocs.com",
          "username": "avigaffa"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-04-08 06:10:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8: Code-Review-1\n\nAgree with Oren. This variable should not be static and it should be local variable instead of class member.\nThe function should not be synchronized",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "966ad7b5408afb2e73cf00f9faac273b945256ae",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2737,
