        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-04-08 06:16:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nHi, Guys\nIt seems that the discussion of whether \"validationVsp is static\" or not is out of scope of this patch. I consider that we can open another JIRA/patch to discuss and track this \"validationVsp is static\" issue. if the final conclusion is \"validationVsp shall not be static\", then this patch will not be valid any more, I will close it.",
        "patchset_number": 8
      },
